{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_05_04",
  "title": "LizNoir 05 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、来た！　こころ、こっちこっち！\nもう、また遅刻なんだから～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you're here! Kokoro‚ over here‚ over here!\nGeez‚ you're late again",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 3.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "あふぅ、眠い……。いきなり呼び出して\nどうしたの、愛",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ I'm sleepy…. Calling me out of the blue like this.\nWhat's up‚ Ai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "初ライブが終わって、やっと休日もらったんだから\nこころはもっと惰眠をむさぼり……すかー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We finally got a day off after our first live‚\nI should be relishing in more sleep…zzz.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "来た途端寝ないでよ！　今朝電話で言ったでしょ？\n初ライブの反省会しなくちゃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't fall asleep as soon as you get here! I told you this morning on the phone!\nWe need to have a review meeting for our first live!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "反省会なんて必要ないよ～～\n大成功だったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We don't need a review meeting\nIt was a huge success‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.32,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "楽屋に戻ったら、莉央さんも葵さんもずーっと\n無言だったよ！　MCでこころが余計なこと言うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we got back to the dressing room‚ both Rio-san and Aoi-san\nstayed silent! It's because you said unnecessary things during the MC.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7633333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "自己紹介しろって言うから\nフツーにしただけだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You told me to introduce myself‚\nso I just did it normally~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5766666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "やっほー！　LizNoirの新センター赤崎こころ\nで～す！　みんなに届け、アイドルスマイル！　って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yahoo~! LizNoir's new center‚ Kokoro Akazaki‚\nat your service~! Sending everyone my idol smile! And then",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんな、大盛り上がりだったよね～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "all the fans were super hyped",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "違うよ！　動揺してざわざわしてたんだよ！\nそれに勝手に他のメンバーの話もしちゃうし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! They were confused and murmuring!\nAnd you just went and talked about the other members without permission…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8866666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "愛の実家がラーメン屋さんなこと？\n別に良くない？　ラーメン好きな人多いよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fact that Ai's family runs a ramen shop?\nWhat's wrong with that? There are tons of people who love ramen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワはプライベートなことは極力話さないって\n決めてたでしょ？　私はともかく先輩方はまずいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We decided that LizNoir wouldn't talk about private things as much as possible‚\nremember? It might be okay for me‚ but it's not okay for our seniors.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんがパンケーキの食べ歩きが趣味だって教えた時\nファンの人達、すっご～く驚いてたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I told everyone that Rio-san's hobby is going around eating pancakes‚\nthe fans were suuuper surprised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "それ、莉央さんが表に出してないことなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Rio-san hasn't revealed that to the public…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんは、なぜこんにゃく嫌いなのか聞いた時\nどうして答えてくれなかったんだろうね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder why Aoi-san didn't answer me when I\nasked why she hates konjac?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "すっごい怒ってたんだよ！　こころ空気読んでよ！\nあ～～、ネットでも私達、叩かれてるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was super mad! Kokoro‚ read the room!\nAgh‚ people are bashing us online too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "愛はこころと違ってお豆腐メンタルだから\nネットは見ない方がいいんじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ you've got a glass heart unlike me‚\nso maybe you shouldn't look at the internet?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言ってる場合じゃないよ！\n私達、リズノワにふさわしくないって言われてるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn't the time to be saying that!\nPeople are saying that we're not fit to be in LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "みんながそういう意見じゃないってば\n親近感が持てたっていうコメントもいっぱいあったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not everyone thinks that‚ you know.\nThere were also lots of comments saying that they felt closer to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.6133333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、リズノワはそういうのいらないって、莉央さんも\n葵さんも言ってたし……ダメだよ勝手なことは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Rio-san and Aoi-san said they didn't need that…\nIt's no good doing things on our own…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "――LizNoirに笑顔はいらない\nキリッ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――LizNoir doesn't need smiles.\nStares intensely",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "ふざけてる場合じゃないでしょ！\nああ、もうこれからどうしよう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn't the time to be joking around!\nUgh‚ what are we going to do now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり私達なんかがLizNoirに入るなんて\n恐れ多いことだったのかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it was too presumptuous for us to join LizNoir after all…\n…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "社長に言って、今からでも私達は抜けた方が――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We should tell the president and leave now‚ even at this late hour――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "何を言ってるの、愛\n愛も私もこのチャンスを絶対、逃しちゃダメだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about‚ Ai?\nNeither of us can let go of this chance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "一年前のこと、忘れたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have you forgotten what happened a year ago?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "――え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "あ～あ、またオーディション落ちちゃった……\nダンスがまだまだって……こころは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ughh‚ I failed the audition again…\nThey said my dancing still needs work… How about you‚ Kokoro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "私も落ちた……\n今回は絶対に自信あったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I failed too…\nI was so confident this time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "後から入った高島さんと木村さんに抜かれちゃったね\nもっとレッスン頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were overtaken by Takashima-san and Kimura-san‚ who joined later than us.\nI have to work harder on my lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 196.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、違う\n私も愛も、あの二人よりずっとダンスはうまいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ that's not it.\nBoth you and I are much better dancers than them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ？\nじゃあ、私達何がいけなかったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?\nThen what did we do wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "私、今回のオーディションで確信した\n歌や踊りがうまくたってデビュー出来ないんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I became certain during this audition.\nYou can't debut just because you can sing and dance well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "高島さんはテレビ局のプロデューサーの娘\n木村さんは、女優のお母さんがいる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Takashima-san is the daughter of a TV producer‚\nand Kimura-san has a mother who's an actress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 223.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待ってよ、こころ！\nそんな言い方、頑張ってる二人に失礼だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hold on a sec‚ Kokoro!\nThat's rude to them! They're working hard!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 229.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "愛は人が良すぎ。コネとか容姿とかが\nやっぱり芸能界では一番大事なんだよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ you're too nice. Connections and looks\nare the most important things in the entertainment world…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 235.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないよ、ほら、私達の好きな\nLizNoirの歌とダンスは凄いじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. Look‚ our beloved LizNoir's singing\nand dancing are amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "ああいう風になろうって誓って\n私達ここで練習ずっと頑張ってきたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We swore to become like them\nand have been working hard at practicing here‚ haven't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
