      "text": "…………愛、私は、もうオーディションに\n落ちたくないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………Ai‚ I…don't want to fail any more auditions.\n落ちたくないよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 255.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "いきなり莉央さんや葵さんのレベルにはなれない\n正攻法じゃいつデビュー出来るか分からない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't suddenly reach Rio-san and Aoi-san's level.\nI don't know when we'll be able to debut if we stick to the straight and narrow…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "だったら邪道でもいい。媚び媚びに媚びまくってでも\n通ってみせる。たとえ愛に失望されても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So even if it means using dirty tactics‚ I'll get through.\nEven if you end up disappointed in me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 272.4
    },
