      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "あれからだったね、こころが\nアイドルスマイルとか言い出したの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's when it started‚\nwhen you started talking about \"idol smiles\".",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_04-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "うん、そのおかげで、朝倉社長直々に\n声を掛けてもらえたんだよ～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ thanks to that‚ Asakura-san himself\nscouted us",
