      "text": "私は直接、社長に声掛けてもらってないもん\nそもそもどうして私なのか分からなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He never directly approached me.\nI didn't even know why he chose me in the first place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 301.5,
